episodes.title: Interview with Ben Braun and Chiaki Yanagimoto for AUM: THE CULT AT THE END OF THE WORLD
episodes.description:
Alise interviews directors Ben Braun and Chiaki Yanagimoto about their documentary, Aum: The Cult at the End of the World that details the story of Shoko Asahara who was the leader of Aum Shinrikyo. We talk about their connection to this story and the way that propaganda can influence people in their darkest moments.
